Package: experiments.experiment1.stack.connector

[Groovy] Class ConnectorToEthernet

      • experiments.experiment1.stack.connector.ConnectorToEthernet
      • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
        PacketReceiver

        class ConnectorToEthernet
extends Connector

        Implementiert das Interface PacketReceiver, so das bei jedem empfangenen Ethernet-Frame die Methode "receivePacket" gerufen wird
